<div class="side-title"> 06.  REFLECTION </div>

<h3 id="what-would-i-have-done-differently">What would I have done differently?</h3>

<p>I had a lot of fun designing a product that solved a problem I‚Äôm constantly having, but I wish I started thinking about the direction I was going after talking to more people and did more user research.  I might have pivoted my direction, who knows?</p>

<p>Some of the UI elements I designed looked good to me back then, but now my design skill is sharpened I would have made different design decisions.</p>

<h3 id="next-steps">Next Steps</h3>

<p>I want to go back and revisit the design and finesse some UI elements, and publish this App.</p>
